## Answer to your question

Yes:

```text
Parallel files? Yes.
Parallel chunks? Yes, with custom controller.
Configurable 4, 5, 6? Yes.
```

For your specific requirement, I would use:

```text
Media files:
Custom chunk controller → on-prem → FFmpeg → WAV → Blob

Other files:
Direct Azure Blob block upload → Blob Storage
```

This is cleaner than forcing Tus for everything.
